    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been such a joy to drive\u2014honestly, it\u2019s perfect for everything from daily commutes to fun weekend road trips! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs beautifully, so it's totally ready to hit the road with you today. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 28900.0,
