    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between a spirited drive and reliable daily transport. The exterior finish holds a high-gloss shine, though closer inspection reveals the expected minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car has been treated with the utmost respect. It features a complete service history, including a recent cooling system refresh and a fresh set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly through the rev range, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean, well-documented history.",
